<div class="sectionHeading" id="logging_in">Logging In</div>

<p>Registering for an account and logging in to Quadbase is easy. Follow the steps below to register and log in to the site.</p>

<ol>
<li>Click the "Sign Up" link in the upper right corner of the home page.<br/><br/>
<center>
<a href="http://quadbase.org/users/sign_up"><%= image_tag("signup.png", {:border => 1})%></a>
</center>
<br/>
</li>
<li>
Fill out the registration form, agree to the site license, and click "Sign up".<br/><br/>
<center>
<a href="http://quadbase.org/users/sign_up"><%= image_tag("signupform.png", {:border => 1})%></a></center>
<br/>
</li>
